Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Daliaon Central Elementary School in the City of Davao to Don Juan Dela Cruz Central Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 668
An Act Changing the Name of the Daliaon Central Elementary School in the City of Davao to Don Juan Dela Cruz Central Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Daliaon Central Elementary School in the City of Davao is changed to Don Juan dela Cruz Central Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
